    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(S) In nomine domini nostri Iehsu Christi dei eterni, anno ab eius
                        nativitate millesimo centesimo octuagesimo quinto, quinto kall. iulii,
                        indictione tertia. Manifesti sumus nos <persName><name
                                ref="Picolus de Lebiano">Picolus</name> de
                                <placeName>Lebiano</placeName></persName> quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Brunus">Brunelli</name></persName> et <persName><name
                                ref="Ermengarda">Mengardina</name></persName> uxor eius et filia
                        quondam <persName><name ref="Widuccius">Guiducii</name></persName> (…) ubi
                        interfuit notitia Aldrici iudicis domni imperatoris (…) per hanc cartulam
                        offerimus tibi deo et <persName><name ref="Petrus">Petro</name></persName>,
                        dei gratia rectori<orgName key="#Hospitals" ref="#juridical_persons/3206">
                            <rs key="#Hospitals">hospitalis</rs> de <placeName key="#Hospitals"
                                ref="#places/3207">Altopasso</placeName></orgName> (…) videlicet
                        nosmet et omnes casas et casinas seu casalinas, terras cultas et incultas,
                        donicatas et massaritias et omnia nostra bona, iura et actiones que nos
                        habemus et nobis aliquo modo vel ordine pertinent seu in antea pertinere
                        debeant, tam de allodiis quam de tenimentis seu libellariis, ceterisque
                        bonis et cum omni iure et actione et repetitione que nobis pertinent contra
                                <persName><name ref="Bonusfilius de Vivinaria">Bonfiliolum</name> de
                                <placeName ref="#places/3211">Vivinaria</placeName></persName>, pro
                        sol. quadraginta bonorum denariorum lucensium quos nobis debet, unde habemus
                        pignus petiam unam de terra que est in <placeName>Corzano</placeName>, que
                        coheret terre filiorum quondam <persName><name ref="Merollare"
                                >Merolari</name></persName> et que habemus, de sex libris bonorum
                        denariorum lucensium quas debent nobis <persName><name
                                ref="Mariscotus da la costa">Marescottus</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name ref="Lotteringus da la costa"
                            >Loteringus</name></persName> germani quondam *** da la costa, et de
                        sol. viginti octo luc. quos <persName><name ref="Silvester da la costa"
                                >Silvester</name></persName> da la costa nobis debet, ut dictum est.
                            <foreign>Pena</foreign>: in duplum (…) sub pena lucensium consulum et
                        treguanorum vel potestatis (…). Actum ad <rs key="#Monasteries"
                            >monasterium</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/3218">sancti
                            Michaelis</orgName> prope <placeName ref="#places/464"
                            key="#Monasteries">Pisciam Maiorem</placeName>. Predicta Mengardina omni
                        suo iuri de predictis rebus sibi aliquo modo pertinenti abrenuntiavi.
                        Predicti iugales posuerunt se in manus predicti rectoris per conversos et
                        offertos et ei obedientiam promiserunt. (…) <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Raginaldus">Rainaldinus</name></persName> quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Wido">Guidi</name></persName> et <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Zabolinus">Zabolinus</name></persName> quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Robertus">Robertini</name></persName> et
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Gherardus"
                            >Girardinus</name></persName> quondam <persName><name ref="Heinricus"
                                >Arigetti</name></persName> et <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Wilicius">Guilicio</name></persName> quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Lambertus">Lamberti</name></persName> rogati <rs key="#Witness"
                            >testes</rs> interfuerunt. Interfuerunt <persName key="#Judge"><name
                                ref="Bonaiunta">Bonaiunta</name></persName> quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Hugolinus">Ugolini</name></persName> et <persName key="#Judge"
                                ><name ref="Cecius">Cecius</name></persName> quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Rodelandus">Rolandi</name></persName> de Sancto Andrea iudices.
                        (S) <persName key="#Writer #Notary #Judge"><name ref="Aldricus"
                                >Aldricus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudex</rs> ac <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> domni Fedrici
                        imperatoris post traditam complevi et dedi.</ab>
